==English==

===Pronunciation===
'''Mess*ene'''
MEH-seen

===Proper noun===
'''Messenia'''
# Also [[Messinia]].  A region in southwestern Peloponnese which has its modern capital at [[Kalamai|Kalamata]].  The original capital was at [[Messene]].

